Tripo is an iOS application designed to enhance travel experiences by helping users discover and explore nearby locations. Key features include:

Location Discovery: Seamlessly find and integrate nearby attractions into travel itineraries.
Chat Functionality: Communicate and share travel experiences with other users via dedicated chat channels.
Tool Section:
Translation: English-to-Chinese translation tool.
Currency Rates: Real-time currency conversion rates.
Gallery: A shared space for photo sharing.
Weather Updates: Current weather information for the userâ€™s location.
Tripo combines these features to provide a comprehensive travel companion app.
